name: TheEndOfTorment †
description: [TheEndOfTorment] is a reflection of the spiritual conflicts I’ve been enduring the last 14 months of my life. Joining the military has taken me away from being fulfilled spiritually. There hasn’t been time to take myself out of the current setting and reconnect with God. A few days ago, I’ve reconnected and invited God back into my heart initiated by the love of my life. It’s time to turn a new chapter of my life and live only through love and light. Thank you for everyone supporting me and giving me the strength to keep going. I will forever be grateful of you. Once I’m settled down in my new duty station, I’ll do a hoodie giveaway. Be on the lookout 👀!
